### Search V1 manual smoke test
### Open this file in IntelliJ IDEA / JetBrains HTTP Client and run requests one by one.

@host = http://localhost:8080
@province = Bangkok
@district = District 1
@checkIn = 2026-04-25
@checkOut = 2026-04-27
@adults = 2
@rooms = 1
@page = 1
@size = 10

### 1. Catalog options
GET {{host}}/api/catalog/options
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Search with recommended sort
GET {{host}}/api/hotels/search?province={{province}}&district={{district}}&checkIn={{checkIn}}&checkOut={{checkOut}}&adults={{adults}}&rooms={{rooms}}&page={{page}}&size={{size}}&sort=recommended
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Search with price ascending
GET {{host}}/api/hotels/search?province={{province}}&district={{district}}&checkIn={{checkIn}}&checkOut={{checkOut}}&adults={{adults}}&rooms={{rooms}}&page={{page}}&size={{size}}&sort=price_asc
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Search with price descending
GET {{host}}/api/hotels/search?province={{province}}&district={{district}}&checkIn={{checkIn}}&checkOut={{checkOut}}&adults={{adults}}&rooms={{rooms}}&page={{page}}&size={{size}}&sort=price_desc
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. Search with rating descending
GET {{host}}/api/hotels/search?province={{province}}&district={{district}}&checkIn={{checkIn}}&checkOut={{checkOut}}&adults={{adults}}&rooms={{rooms}}&page={{page}}&size={{size}}&sort=rating_desc
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. Search without district
GET {{host}}/api/hotels/search?province={{province}}&checkIn={{checkIn}}&checkOut={{checkOut}}&adults={{adults}}&rooms={{rooms}}&page={{page}}&size={{size}}&sort=recommended
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. Search with hotel type + room filters
GET {{host}}/api/hotels/search?province={{province}}&checkIn={{checkIn}}&checkOut={{checkOut}}&adults={{adults}}&rooms={{rooms}}&page={{page}}&size={{size}}&sort=recommended&hotelTypes=RESORT&roomCategories=SUITE&bedTypes=DOUBLE&roomAmenities=BALCONY
Accept: application/json

###

### 8. Search with hotel + room amenities
GET {{host}}/api/hotels/search?province={{province}}&checkIn={{checkIn}}&checkOut={{checkOut}}&adults={{adults}}&rooms={{rooms}}&page={{page}}&size={{size}}&sort=recommended&hotelAmenities=POOL&roomAmenities=BALCONY
Accept: application/json

###

### 9. Search page 2
GET {{host}}/api/hotels/search?province={{province}}&district={{district}}&checkIn={{checkIn}}&checkOut={{checkOut}}&adults={{adults}}&rooms={{rooms}}&page=2&size={{size}}&sort=recommended
Accept: application/json

###

### 10. Validation check: invalid date range
GET {{host}}/api/hotels/search?province={{province}}&district={{district}}&checkIn={{checkOut}}&checkOut={{checkIn}}&adults={{adults}}&rooms={{rooms}}&page={{page}}&size={{size}}&sort=recommended
Accept: application/json

###

### 11. Hotel detail
### Replace 1 with a hotelId returned from a search response.
GET {{host}}/api/hotels/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 12. Available rooms for a hotel
### Replace 1 with a hotelId returned from a search response.
GET {{host}}/api/hotels/1/available-rooms?checkIn={{checkIn}}&checkOut={{checkOut}}&adults={{adults}}&rooms={{rooms}}
Accept: application/json

